#: templates/About_Us.html:70
msgid ""
"Welcome to <strong>MySeries</strong> – your ultimate hub for discovering,"
" tracking, and enjoying the\n"
"            latest and greatest TV shows and anime. We’re a small but "
"passionate team of enthusiasts who believe that\n"
"            every series, from hidden gems to global hits, deserves to be"
" seen."
msgstr ""

#: templates/About_Us.html:75
msgid ""
"Our mission is simple: to make your series-watching experience seamless "
"and fun. Whether you’re\n"
"            hunting for the next binge-worthy anime or keeping up with "
"popular dramas, we provide the tools and\n"
"            inspiration to explore your favorites."
msgstr ""

#: templates/About_Us.html:80
msgid ""
"At MySeries, we value quality, passion, and community. We constantly "
"update our database with new\n"
"            releases, detailed series info, and high-quality cover "
"images. Our goal is to create a place where series\n"
"            lovers can find everything they need, all in one spot."
msgstr ""

#: templates/About_Us.html:85
msgid ""
"Thank you for being part of our journey. Sit back, explore, and let "
"MySeries help you find your next\n"
"            favorite show!"
msgstr ""

